of prices and currencies,

00:28:17.165 --> 00:28:19.320
or that sharing of
information via mobile.

00:28:19.320 --> 00:28:21.880
So absolutely, I think
that's very, very much

00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:23.640
a huge part of the future.

