00:28:45.390 --> 00:28:46.400
a lot of creativity.

00:28:46.400 --> 00:28:47.900
What's your advice
for entrepreneurs

00:28:47.900 --> 00:28:50.170
looking to get started?

00:28:50.170 --> 00:29:01.117
YOANI SANCHEZ:
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

00:29:01.117 --> 00:29:03.700
TRANSLATOR: Just a few days ago,
when I spoke at Google Ideas,

00:29:03.700 --> 00:29:07.420
I said that creativity is having
the possibility of opening

00:29:07.420 --> 00:29:09.310
a window when the
door is closed.

00:29:09.310 --> 00:29:12.316
YOANI SANCHEZ:
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

00:29:12.316 --> 00:29:15.160
TRANSLATOR: And creativity
is also necessity's daughter.

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:21.810
YOANI SANCHEZ:
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

00:29:21.810 --> 00:29:24.150
